tle":"","runtime":83,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"A father is imprisoned after committing a brutal revenge crime. During his confinement he must adapt to a new life of abuse, including injury and humiliation by guards and other prisoners."},"name":"English","iso_639_1":"en","iso_3166_1":"US","english_name":"English"},{"data":{"title":"Za murami Śmierci","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Misael trafia do więzienia. Za kratami królują przemoc i okrucieństwo, a ludzkie życie jest warte mniej niż rozmowa telefoniczna. Władcą tego świata jest bezwzględny naczelnik, widzący w Misaelu łatwą ofiarę. Nie mógł wiedzieć, jak bardzo się mylił."},"name":"Polski","iso_639_1":"pl","iso_3166_1":"PL","english_name":"Polish"},{"data":{"title":"Za zdmi smrti - Krvavá pomsta","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Otec, který je uvězněn poté, co spáchal brutální zločin pomsty. Přizpůsobuje se novému životu zneužívání, včetně zranění a ponižování ze strany stráží a dalších vězňů."},"name":"Český","iso_639_1":"cs","iso_3166_1":"CZ","english_name":"Czech"},{"data":{"title":"A halál falai mögött","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Miután Misael bosszút áll gyermeke gyilkosán, előzetes letartóztatásban várja a bírói ítéletet. A börtönben a gyászoló apának szembe kell néznie a rabok erőszakos kegyetlenségével és a fegyőrök általi kíméletlen megaláztatásokkal, miközben korábbi élete családja eltávolodásával fakó emlékké halványul. A kiábrándult, magára maradt férfi a börtön kutyájában, Sarnában talál barátra."},"name":"Magyar","iso_639_1":"hu","iso_3166_1":"HU","english_name":"Hungarian"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Un padre es encarcelado tras cometer un brutal crimen de venganza. Durante su confinamiento debe adaptarse a una nueva vida de abusos, incluyendo lesiones y humillaciones por parte de los guardias y otros presos."},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"ES","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"黑血","runtime":86,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"该片是英年早逝的美国演员瑞凡·菲尼克斯的未竟遗作：试图通过第二趟蜜月挽救婚姻危机的好莱坞夫妇因汽车抛锚搁浅于荒漠，在这片宛若末日的犹他州不毛之地，一名有着印地安血统的男子独居在核试爆区的小屋，他的妻子曾经因核辐射引发的癌症而丧命。此时，因有了夫妻两人的短暂陪伴，他竟渴望起更亲密的关系，从而渐渐演变成一场情仇血案。导演乔治·斯鲁依泽在片头表示，这部电影就像一张只有两条腿的椅子，剪辑赋予了它第三条腿，虽然第四条腿永远不在了，但椅子依然能够站着。（小易甫字幕组）"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"CN","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Bir baba acımasız bir intikam suçu işledikten sonra hapsedilir. Tutukluluğu sırasında, gardiyanlar ve diğer mahkumlar tarafından yaralanma ve aşağılanma dahil olmak üzere yeni bir taciz hayatına uyum sağlamalıdır."},"name":"Türkçe","iso_639_1":"tr","iso_3166_1":"TR","english_name":"Turkish"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Een vader wordt gevangengezet nadat hij een brute wraakmisdaad heeft begaan. Tijdens zijn gevangenschap moet hij zich aanpassen aan een nieuw leven vol misbruik, inclusief verwondingen en vernedering door bewakers en andere gevangenen."},"name":"Nederlands","iso_639_1":"nl","iso_3166_1":"NL","english_name":"Dutch"}],"reviews_tmdb":[],"recommendations":[{"id":294793,"adult":false,"title":"All the Old Knives","video":false,"overview":"When the CIA discovers one of its agents leaked information that cost more than 100 people their lives, veteran operative Henry Pelham is assigned to root out the mole with his former lover and colleague Celia Harrison.","genre_ids":[53,9648],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.6151,"vote_count":610,"poster_path":"/g4tMniKxol1TBJrHlAtiDjjlx4Q.jpg","release_date":"2022-04-08","vote_average":5.993,"backdrop_path":"/xicKILMzPn6XZYCOpWwaxlUzg6S.jpg","original_title":"All the Old Knives","original_language":"en"},{"id":568124,"adult":false,"title":"Encanto","video":false,"overview":"The tale of an extraordinary family, the Madrigals, who live hidden in the mountains of Colombia, in a magical house, in a vibrant town, in a wondrous, charmed place called an Encanto. The magic of the Encanto has blessed every child in the family—every child except one, Mirabel. But when she discovers that the magic surrounding the Encanto is in danger, Mirabel decides that she, the only ordinary Madrigal, might just be her exceptional family's last hope.","genre_ids":[16,35,10751,14],"media_type":"movie","popularity":12.6352,"vote_count":10066,"poster_path":"/4j0PNHkMr5ax3IA8tjtxcmPU3QT.jpg","release_date":"2021-10-13","vote_average":7.572,"backdrop_path":"/3G1Q5xF40HkUBJXxt2DQgQzKTp5.jpg","original_title":"Encanto","original_language":"en"},{"id":674,"adult":false,"title":"Harry Potter and the Goblet of Fire","video":false,"overview":"When Harry Potter's name emerges from the Goblet of Fire, he becomes a competitor in a grueling battle for glory among three wizarding schools—the Triwizard Tournament. But since Harry never submitted his name for the Tournament, who did? Now Harry must confront a deadly dragon, fierce water demons and an enchanted maze only to find himself in the cruel grasp of He Who Must Not Be Named.","genre_ids":[12,14],"media_type":"movie","popularity":18.0915,"vote_count":21879,"poster_path":"/fECBtHlr0RB3foNHDiCBXeg9Bv9.jpg","release_date":"2005-11-16","vote_average":7.801,"backdrop_path":"/8f9dnOtpArDrOMEylpSN9Sc6fuz.jpg","original_title":"Harry Potter and the Goblet of Fire","original_language":"en"},{"id":671,"adult":false,"title":"Harry Potter and the Philosopher's Stone","video":false,"overview":"Harry Potter has lived under the stairs at his aunt and uncle's house his whole life. But on his 11th birthday, he learns he's a powerful wizard—with a place waiting for him at the Hogwarts School of Witchcraft and Wizardry. As he learns to harness his newfound powers with the help of the school's kindly headmaster, Harry uncovers the truth about his parents' deaths—and about the villain who's to blame.","genre_ids":[12,14],"media_type":"movie","popularity":22.4943,"vote_count":29183,"poster_path":"/wuMc08IPKEatf9rnMNXvIDxqP4W.jpg","release_date":"2001-11-16","vote_average":7.899,"backdrop_path":"/1XAC6RPT01UX9EQGy2JVn5c8pgy.jpg","original_title":"Harry Potter and the Philosopher's Stone","original_language":"en"},{"id":872585,"adult":false,"title":"Oppenheimer","video":false,"overview":"The story of J. Robert Oppenheimer's role in the development of the atomic bomb during World War II.","genre_ids":[18,36],"media_type":"movie","popularity":23.0611,"vote_count":11386,"poster_path":"/8Gxv8gSFCU0XGDykEGv7zR1n2ua.jpg","release_date":"2023-07-19","vote_average":8.034,"backdrop_path":"/ycnO0cjsAROSGJKuMODgRtWsHQw.jpg","original_title":"Oppenheimer","original_language":"en"},{"id":76600,"adult":false,"title":"Avatar: The Way of Water","video":false,"overview":"Set more than a decade after the events of the first film, learn the story of the Sully family (Jake, Neytiri, and their kids), the trouble that follows them, the lengths they go to keep each other safe, the battles they fight to stay alive, and the tragedies they endure.","genre_ids":[28,12,878],"media_type":"movie","popularity":36.0964,"vote_count":13743,"poster_path":"/t6HIqrRAclMCA60NsSmeqe9RmNV.jpg","release_date":"2022-12-14","vote_average":7.598,"backdrop_path":"/cd8YDn7M0lfaHhZdU6MvCDxPalP.jpg","original_title":"Avatar: The Way of Water","original_language":"en"},{"id":436969,"adult":false,"title":"The Suicide Squad","video":false,"overview":"Supervillains Harley Quinn, Bloodsport, Peacemaker and a collection of nutty cons at Belle Reve prison join the super-secret, super-shady Task Force X as they are dropped off at the remote, enemy-infused island of Corto Maltese.","genre_ids":[28,35,12],"media_type":"movie","popularity":11.8868,"vote_count":9400,"poster_path":"/q61qEyssk2ku3okWICKArlAdhBn.jpg","release_date":"2021-07-28","vote_average":7.468,"backdrop_path":"/jlGmlFOcfo8n5tURmhC7YVd4Iyy.jpg","original_title":"The Suicide Squad","original_language":"en"},{"id":673,"adult":false,"title":"Harry Potter and the Prisoner of Azkaban","video":false,"overview":"Year three at Hogwarts means new fun and challenges as Harry learns the delicate art of approaching a Hippogriff, transforming shape-shifting Boggarts into hilarity and even turning back time. But the term also brings danger: soul-sucking Dementors hover over the school, an ally of the accursed He-Who-Cannot-Be-Named lurks within the castle walls, and fearsome wizard Sirius Black escapes Azkaban. And Harry will confront them all.","genre_ids":[12,14],"media_type":"movie","popularity":18.7015,"vote_count":22861,"poster_path":"/aWxwnYoe8p2d2fcxOqtvAtJ72Rw.jpg","release_date":"2004-05-31","vote_average":8.008,"backdrop_path":"/vbk5CfaAHOjQPSAcYm6AoRRz2Af.jpg","original_title":"Harry Potter and the Prisoner of Azkaban","original_language":"en"},{"id":508442,"adult":false,"title":"Soul","video":false,"overview":"Joe Gardner is a middle school teacher with a love for jazz music. After a successful audition at the Half Note Club, he suddenly gets into an accident that separates his soul from his body and is transported to the You Seminar, a center in which souls develop and gain passions before being transported to a newborn child. Joe must enlist help from the other souls-in-training, like 22, a soul who has spent eons in the You Seminar, in order to get back to Earth.","genre_ids":[16,10751,35,14,18,10402],"media_type":"movie","popularity":11.8533,"vote_count":11202,"poster_path":"/6jmppcaubzLF8wkXM36ganVISCo.jpg","release_date":"2020-12-25","vote_average":8.097,"backdrop_path":"/rQaHA74pevnGsxcKGaoZVGWe9TC.jpg","original_title":"Soul","original_language":"en"},{"id":346698,"adult":false,"title":"Barbie","video":false,"overview":"Barbie and Ken are having the time of their lives in the colorful and seemingly perfect world of Barbie Land. However, when they get a chance to go to the real world, they soon discover the joys and perils of living among humans.","genre_ids":[35,12],"media_type":"movie","popularity":19.1444,"vote_count":10795,"poster_path":"/iuFNMS8U5cb6xfzi51Dbkovj7vM.jpg","release_date":"2023-07-19","vote_average":6.929,"backdrop_path":"/ctMserH8g2SeOAnCw5gFjdQF8mo.jpg","original_title":"Barbie","original_language":"en"},{"id":495764,"adult":false,"title":"Birds of Prey (and the Fantabulous Emancipation of One Harley Quinn)","video":false,"overview":"Harley Quinn joins forces with a singer, an assassin and a police detective to help a young girl who had a hit placed on her after she stole a rare diamond from a crime lord.","genre_ids":[28,80],"media_type":"movie","popularity":6.253,"vote_count":10692,"poster_path":"/h4VB6m0RwcicVEZvzftYZyKXs6K.jpg","release_date":"2020-02-05","vote_average":6.884,"backdrop_path":"/uozb2VeD87YmhoUP1RrGWfzuCrr.jpg","original_title":"Birds of Prey (and the Fantabulous Emancipation of One Harley Quinn)","original_language":"en"},{"id":297222,"adult":false,"title":"PK","video":false,"overview":"A stranger in the city asks questions no one has asked before. Known only by his initials, the man's innocent questions and childlike curiosity take him on a journey of love, laughter and letting go.","genre_ids":[35,18,878],"media_type":"movie","popularity":7.0848,"vote_count":1122,"poster_path":"/z2x2Y4tncefsIU7h82gmUM5vnBJ.jpg","release_date":"2014-12-18","vote_average":7.698,"backdrop_path":"/gxfvtq5eYiClS2X7hxAAPBNrbWA.jpg","original_title":"पीके","original_language":"hi"},{"id":663712,"adult":false,"title":"Terrifier 2","video":false,"overview":"A year after the Miles County massacre, Art the Clown is resurrected by a sinister entity. Art returns home, where he must hunt down and destroy teenage Sienna and her younger brother Jonathan on Halloween. As the body count rises, the siblings fight to stay alive while uncovering the true nature of Art's evil intent.","genre_ids":[27,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":5.2892,"vote_count":2430,"poster_path":"/qEAlwXbYk6IHA4ztoS2XFFaa7Xo.jpg","release_date":"2022-10-06","vote_average":6.683,"backdrop_path":"/4QJtcL4D3abqdX6Snrk8ciRkroa.jpg","original_title":"Terrifier 2","original_language":"en"},{"id":363088,"adult":false,"title":"Ant-Man and the Wasp","video":false,"overview":"Just when his time under house arrest is about to end, Scott Lang once again puts his freedom at risk to help Hope van Dyne and Dr. Hank Pym dive into the quantum realm and try to accomplish, against time and any chance of success, a very dangerous rescue mission.","genre_ids":[28,12,878],"media_type":"movie","popularity":7.8312,"vote_count":14004,"poster_path":"/cFQEO687n1K6umXbInzocxcnAQz.jpg","release_date":"2018-07-04","vote_average":6.905,"backdrop_path":"/2tcTm5oRlRN5fKFvY4Gbrwp8h38.jpg","original_title":"Ant-Man and the Wasp","original_language":"en"},{"id":597,"adult":false,"title":"Titanic","video":false,"overview":"101-year-old Rose DeWitt Bukater tells the story of her life aboard the Titanic, 84 years later. A young Rose boards the ship with her mother and fiancé. Meanwhile, Jack Dawson and Fabrizio De Rossi win third-class tickets aboard the ship. Rose tells the whole story from Titanic's departure through to its death—on its first and last voyage—on April 15, 1912.","genre_ids":[18,10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":30.0131,"vote_count":26824,"poster_path":"/9xjZS2rlVxm8SFx8kPC3aIGCOYQ.jpg","release_date":"1997-12-18","vote_average":7.903,"backdrop_path":"/xnHVX37XZEp33hhCbYlQFq7ux1J.jpg","original_title":"Titanic","original_language":"en"},{"id":767,"adult":false,"title":"Harry Potter and the Half-Blood Prince","video":false,"overview":"As Lord Voldemort tightens his grip on both the Muggle and wizarding worlds, Hogwarts is no longer a safe haven. Harry suspects perils may even lie within the castle, but Dumbledore is more intent upon preparing him for the final battle fast approaching. Together they work to find the key to unlock Voldemorts defenses and to this end, Dumbledore recruits his old friend and colleague Horace Slughorn, whom he believes holds crucial information. Even as the decisive showdown looms, romance blossoms for Harry, Ron, Hermione and their classmates. Love is in the air, but danger lies ahead and Hogwarts may never be the same again.","genre_ids":[12,14],"media_type":"movie","popularity":15.5201,"vote_count":20515,"poster_path":"/z7uo9zmQdQwU5ZJHFpv2Upl30i1.jpg","release_date":"2009-07-15","vote_average":7.681,"backdrop_path":"/ze6Mx4QE5mQVXRYmG2flncqqle4.jpg","original_title":"Harry Potter and the Half-Blood Prince","original_language":"en"},{"id":414906,"adult":false,"title":"The Batman","video":false,"overview":"In his second year of fighting crime, Batman uncovers corruption in Gotham City that connects to his own family while facing a serial killer known as the Riddler.","genre_ids":[80,9648,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":16.376,"vote_count":11641,"poster_path":"/74xTEgt7R36Fpooo50r9T25onhq.jpg","release_date":"2022-03-01","vote_average":7.656,"backdrop_path":"/rvtdN5XkWAfGX6xDuPL6yYS2seK.jpg","original_title":"The Batman","original_language":"en"},{"id":264660,"adult":false,"title":"Ex Machina","video":false,"overview":"Caleb, a coder at the world's largest internet company, wins a competition to spend a week at a private mountain retreat belonging to Nathan, the reclusive CEO of the company. But when Caleb arrives at the remote location he finds that he will have to participate in a strange and fascinating experiment in which he must interact with the world's first true artificial intelligence, housed in the body of a beautiful robot girl.","genre_ids":[18,878],"media_type":"movie","popularity":7.9469,"vote_count":14040,"poster_path":"/dmJW8IAKHKxFNiUnoDR7JfsK7Rp.jpg","release_date":"2015-01-21","vote_average":7.573,"backdrop_path":"/uqOuJ50EtTj7kkDIXP8LCg7G45D.jpg","original_title":"Ex Machina","original_language":"en"},{"id":545611,"adult":false,"title":"Everything Everywhere All at Once","video":false,"overview":"An aging Chinese immigrant is swept up in an insane adventure, where she alone can save what's important to her by connecting with the lives she could have led in other universes.","genre_ids":[28,12,878],"media_type":"movie","popularity":11.7985,"vote_count":7694,"poster_path":"/u68AjlvlutfEIcpmbYpKcdi09ut.jpg","release_date":"2022-03-24","vote_average":7.721,"backdrop_path":"/ss0Os3uWJfQAENILHZUdX8Tt1OC.jpg","original_title":"Everything Everywhere All at Once","original_language":"en"},{"id":284054,"adult":false,"title":"Black Panther","video":false,"overview":"King T'Challa returns home to the reclusive, technologically advanced African nation of Wakanda to serve as his country's new leader. However, T'Challa soon finds that he is challenged for the throne by factions within his own country as well as without. Using powers reserved to Wakandan kings, T'Challa assumes the Black Panther mantle to join with ex-girlfriend Nakia, the queen-mother, his princess-kid sister, members of the Dora Milaje (the Wakandan 'special forces') and an American secret agent, to prevent Wakanda from being dragged into a world war.","genre_ids":[28,12,878],"media_type":"movie","popularity":14.4103,"vote_count":23206,"poster_path":"/uxzzxijgPIY7slzFvMotPv8wjKA.jpg","release_date":"2018-02-13","vote_average":7.362,"backdrop_path":"/19Ed4XgjahPm4U8JT7SnntERIlt.jpg","original_title":"Black Panther","original_language":"en"}],"similar_content":[],"external_ids":{"imdb_id":"tt14773112","twitter_id":null,"facebook_id":null,"wikidata_id":null,"instagram_id":null},"social_ids":{"twitter":null,"facebook":null,"instagram":null},"gdvg_id":148327,"wiki_plot":null,"wiki_synopsis":null,"wiki_episode_guide":null,"wiki_production":null,"wiki_cast_notes":null,"wiki_reception":null,"wiki_soundtrack":null,"wiki_release":null,"wiki_accolades":null,"release_dates":[{"iso_3166_1":"GB","release_dates":[{"note":"","type":4,"iso_639_1":"","descriptors":[],"release_date":"2022-06-15T00:00:00.000Z","certification":"15"}]},{"iso_3166_1":"PL","release_dates":[{"note":"","type":4,"